These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, pear, cauliflower, garlic
1. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | eggplant | pear | cauliflower | garlic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda, lemonade
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | cola | lemonade | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, magic-tricks, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | magic-tricks | board-games | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, sports, fantasy, martial-arts
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | action | martial-arts | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, baseball, swimming, sailing
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | sailing | swimming | baseball | skateboarding |

