.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, zucchini, watermelon, radish
1. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating cabbage and the person eating radish##2
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
4. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | radish | zucchini | cabbage | watermelon |

